wp-content/uploads/2024/07/the-last-dinner-party-blondie@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/the-last-dinner-party-blondie@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/the-last-dinner-party-blondie@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/the-last-dinner-party-blondie@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">The Last Evening Party</a>为澳大利亚广播公司 Triple j 的<em>Like A Version</em>系列翻唱了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blondie">Blondie</a>的《Call Me》。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-the-last-dinner-party-interview-prelude-to-ecstasy-3552625">封面上的最后晚宴：巴洛克流行音乐的新加冕君主</a></strong></li></ul><p><em><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-the-last-dinner-party-interview-prelude-to-ecstasy-3552625">NME 封面</a></em>明星对 Blondie 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/debbie-harry">Debbie Harry</a>经典音乐的独特演绎让乐队将 Blondie 更朋克倾向的摇滚品牌换成了他们获得专利的独立风格。请听下面 The Last Evening Party 翻唱的 Blondie 的《Call Me》。 </p><p><iframe title="《The Last Evening Party》翻唱 Blondie 的《Call Me》Like A 版本" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/UiCt0n-lqys?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>主唱阿比盖尔·莫里斯（Abigail Morris）和贝斯手乔治亚·戴维斯（Georgia Davies）在接受 Triple J 采访时谈到为什么选择这首歌作为封面，他们解释说他们过去常常在卡拉 OK 时将这首歌作为“首选”歌曲。莫里斯说：“我们会在家庭聚会上毁掉它并清理房间。这是我们努力挽回这些年来的成果并把它做好。” </p><p><iframe title="《The Last Evening Party》封面 Blondie 的《Call Me》Like A Version 背后（采访）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ydIqIDr06SA?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>该封面<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mercury-prize-2024-check-out-the-shortlisted-nominees-here-3777869">是在乐队宣布入围</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/mercury-prize">2024 年水星奖</a>入围名单后发布的。 2024 年水星奖的总获奖者将于 9 月揭晓，该奖项的广播合作伙伴 BBC 音乐将提供电视和广播报道。</p><p> 3 月，The Last Evening Party 接受 NME 采访，谈论新材料以及他们在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/brit-awards">2024 年全英音乐节上</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-on-the-response-to-debut-album-and-st-vincent-inspiration-3596430"><em>的</em>首张专辑的反响</a>——<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-brits-announce-2024-rising-star-winner-3555457">在获得新星奖</a>前不久。</p><p> “唱片一出来，我们就直接开始巡演，”莫里斯解释道。 “这是我们做过的最好的巡演，因为这是人们第一次知道所有事情的歌词。真的非常非常美丽。”她谈到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-want-snoop-dogg-to-feature-on-big-dog-3581899">另一首尚未发行的歌曲“Big Dog”</a> ，该歌曲已在 TLDP 的演出中现场演奏。您可以在上面观看<em>NME</em>的完整视频采访。 </p><figure id="attachment_3771603" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3771603" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3771603" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The-Last-Dinner-Party-Glastonbury-2024-credit-Andy-Ford-NME@2000x1270.jpg" alt="2024 年格拉斯顿伯里最后的晚宴派对现场，摄影：Andy Ford" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The-Last-Dinner-Party-Glastonbury-2024-credit-Andy-Ford-NME@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The-Last-Dinner-Party-Glastonbury-2024-credit-Andy-Ford-NME@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The-Last-Dinner-Party-Glastonbury-2024-credit-Andy-Ford-NME@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The-Last-Dinner-Party-Glastonbury-2024-credit-Andy-Ford-NME@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The-Last-Dinner-Party-Glastonbury-2024-credit-Andy-Ford-NME@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The-Last-Dinner-Party-Glastonbury-2024-credit-Andy-Ford-NME@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3771603" class="wp-caption-text"> 《最后的晚宴派对》于 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里现场直播。图片来源：Andy Ford for NME</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-announce-autumn-2024-european-tour-3755882">《最后的晚宴》将于今年秋天开始欧洲头条巡演</a>。继在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/roskilde-festival-completes-2024-line-up-with-53-new-acts-including-21-savage-and-pinkpantheress-3615448">Roskilde</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/foo-fighters-and-dua-lipa-announced-as-rock-werchter-2024-headliners-3537761">Rock Werchter</a>演出之后，今年夏天他们还将在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/trnsmt-2024-liam-gallagher-gerry-cinmamon-calvin-harris-lead-line-up-3545593">TRNSMT</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-leeds-2024-full-stage-times-line-up-3765102#:~:text=The%202024%20edition%20of%20Reading,into%20the%20current%20media%20landscape.">Reading &amp; Leeds</a>演出。</p><p> 1 月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-crowned-bbc-sound-of-2024-winners-3565767">乐队荣获 BBC Sound Of 2024 民意调查冠军</a>。他们此前曾入选<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-radar/the-nme-100-essential-emerging-artists-for-2023-radar-3372061">2023 年 NME 100</a>榜单，该榜单列出了未来一年最重要的新兴艺术家。</p><p> 2023 年底， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-were-trying-to-ignore-the-words-hype-and-buzzy-band-3554464">The Last Evening Party 表示，他们在反思自己的巨大崛起时，“试图忽略‘炒作’和‘热闹乐队’这两个词”</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-cover-blondies-call-me-for-like-a-version-3778177">The Last Evening Party 翻唱 Blondie 的《Call Me》的《Like A Version》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
