w.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Gojiratour-news-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-2983194" class="wp-caption-text">哥吉拉现场表演。图片来源：盖蒂</figcaption></figure><p>这场表演将标志着迪翁四年多来首次登上舞台，此前她被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/celine-dion-reveals-stiff-person-syndrome-diagnosis-reschedules-and-cancels-shows-3363354">诊断出患有僵人综合症</a>——一种罕见的慢性神经系统疾病，会导致肌肉僵硬和剧烈痉挛。</p><p>她最后一次登上舞台是在2020年，当时她在纽约演出，去年她原计划进行世界巡演，但<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/celine-dion-reveals-stiff-person-syndrome-diagnosis-reschedules-and-cancels-shows-3363354">由于病情而被迫取消了所有预定的日期</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/row-erupts-from-far-right-over-aya-nakamura-performing-at-paris-olympics-3602225">据传，法国非洲节奏明星中村绫也卷入了一场因她的加入而引发的极右争吵中</a>。</p><p>与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/korn-announce-30th-anniversary-stadium-show-with-evanescence-gojira-scars-on-broadway-and-more-3597555">Gojira 将于 10 月 5 日星期六在洛杉矶 BMO 体育场举行的 KoRn 30 周年体育场演出中亮相</a>。</p><p>他们将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/evanescence">《伊凡塞斯》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/scars-on-broadway-1334362">《百老汇疤痕》、</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/spiritbox">《Spiritbox》</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/scars-on-broadway-1334362">、</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/vended">《Vending》</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/scars-on-broadway-1334362">和《达伦·马拉基安》</a>一起演出—— <a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fkorn-tickets%2Fartist%2F775700" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处购买门票</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gojira-will-perform-at-the-2024-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony-3778120">哥吉拉将在 2024 年巴黎奥运会开幕式上表演的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
